  <source>Second Military Medical University</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators had performed more than 250 cases of breast approach endoscopic
      thyroidectomy (BAET). The goal of this study is to evaluate whether BAET could be a minimally
      invasive procedure under the expert's hands.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
